ction values\n- Top-level interpolated JSON values\n- Custom `Encoder` and `KeyEncoder` usage for interpolated object values and keys\n\nPer instruction, I did not compile or run the tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0cfab3af810a93330169fa5aca87048196bd4cb4383d551754\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1329, "output": 903, "cacheRead": 45568, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 47800, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778014906658, "responseId": "resp_0cfab3af810a93330169fa5abb69d4819686f0987c03d1acb2"}}
